author: Benjamin Weiser and William K. Rashbaum
description: The ex-congressman, whose wife, Huma Abedin, was a top aide to Hillary Clinton, will plead guilty to a single charge of transferring obscene material to a minor.
title: Anthony Weiner to Plead Guilty to Resolve Sexting Inquiry

author: Doug Stanglin
description: The former Congressman, who is separated from Hillary Clinton aide Huma Abedin, could face a prison term and must register as a sex offender.
title: Former Congressman Anthony Weiner pleads guilty to sexting with minor

author: Andrew Buncombe
description: Disgraced former Democratic congressman Anthony Weiner is reportedly to plead guilty to a charge of sending obscene material to a minor, after federal authorities launched a “sexting” investigation.  The former political high-flyer and estranged husband of senior Hillary Clinton, Huma Abedin, is scheduled to appear in a New York court.
title: Anthony Weiner 'to plead guilty' after being accused of sexting a minor
